result.formatted_address: G/F,, 28 Jervois St, Sheung Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: Knead

reviews.text:
I ordered two big lunch sets for a junk last week. Everything looked amazing, was very fresh and tasted yummy. All of my friends enjoyed it and there was something for everyone. 
I also regularly come into the shop for my lunch or a quick afternoon snack.

By far the best junk food package out there- delicious food well presented with a wide variety of options. Great organisation from the team and prompt delivery. Will most certainly be using them for events and junks again in the future.

Good concept, but there is still much to improve. The products are okay, but not of high quality. The store is very hot despite the A / C. Finally, the staff is unfriendly and they are mainly concerned with themselves or their phone.

If you have cravings for a sandwich, Knead is a good option, as long as you don't expect a great experience.

Really great experience with Knead providing breakfast and lunch services for our events in Hong Kong last week. 4 deliveries in total across 2 different event sites and everything was ordered on time and to a high standard. Would recommend anyone using Knead.
Really good salad, freshly made. Also friendly people and a lot to individual choose from. Can strongly recommend to eat there, it's definitely something healthy.
